In media

[The Weather Channel](/The_Weather_Channel) notably recalled the 1977 [Toccoa Falls](/Toccoa_Falls) dam break and subsequent flood. &#91;48&#93;

On May 7, 2000, Mary Ann Stephens of Toccoa was tragically killed outside a [Ramada Inn](/Ramada_Inn) in [Jacksonville, Florida](/Jacksonville,_Florida) during a vacation with her husband. This incident garnered national attention and was the subject of the Academy Award-winning French documentary, [Murder on a Sunday Morning](/Murder_on_a_Sunday_Morning), which explored the arrest and eventual acquittal of the initially accused suspect. &#91;49&#93;

